div.div:
Echoes SSH_PUB_KEY to the authorised hosts file to enable SSH from my Local PC.
Goes back to auto_deploy, echoes the FAUNA_DB_KEY, GITHUB_TOKEN, API_URL & EMAIL_PASS to a .env file, runs `docker-compose up -d` for starting the services, removes the default nginx config file and copies server.conf to nginx config directory for url mapping of api and app (website).
Lastly, schedules a script with a delay of 5mins to run certbot to generate ssl certificates for api and app subdomains and that triggers another script to constantly monitor for changes in the origin repos of api, website and givemyresume.github.io and pull accordingly if change occurs.
